# Student Performance Analysis

A student performance analysis system built from scratch using only NumPy.

## What it does
- Calculates average marks per student
- Calculates average marks per subject
- Identifies top and lowest scorer
- Classifies students as Pass or Fail
- Assigns grades based on performance

## Pass/Fail Rule
A student fails if they score below 40 in ANY subject
regardless of their overall average.

## Grade Scale
- A = 80 to 100
- B = 60 to 79
- C = 40 to 59
- D = 20 to 39
- F = 0 to 19

## How to run

1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies
   pip install -r requirements.txt
3. Run the project
   python main.py

## Project Structure
- data/ — generates student marks data
- analysis/ — statistics and grade logic
- main.py — connects everything together

## Built With
- Python
- NumPy




